9
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:52,000
watching fictional detectives on TV. These programs are called murder mysteries and tell the story

10
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:58,799
of a detective solving a crime. In 2020, a magazine called The Radio Times asked readers

11
00:00:58,799 --> 00:01:05,920
who their favourite TV detective was. So, who do you think was the most popular? Was it A, Sherlock

12
