14
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:26,079
crimes in the real world, their techniques are often quite different from what we see on television.

15
00:01:26,079 --> 00:01:32,239
Yes, solving crimes involves collecting and reviewing lots of evidence, like DNA,

16
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:40,799
fingerprints or CCTV. All of this work takes a lot of time, so can AI help police speed up the work

17
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:46,639
and even solve crimes? That's the question listener Alistair had for the BBC Radio 4 program,

18
